WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Let's talk about headings and

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
accessibility.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Now, in order to get your online content

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
in Canvas accessible, you need to designate headings

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.000
for any of your pages.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Now, this example here,

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
this urban gardening lesson, as I scroll through,

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.000
as a sighted person, I can pretty

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.000
easily pick up on the organization and

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.000
structure of this lesson.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.000
I can also really easily scroll through

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.000
and find something maybe that I need

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
to go over a second time.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.000
But this particular lesson

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.000
doesn't have any headings designated,

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.000
which means that if instead

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.000
I was using some sort of assistive technology,

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:43.000
instead of my eyes, like a screen

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.000
reader, to get to this information,

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.000
the screen reader would just plow right

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.000
through all of this information and make

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.000
it seem like it was all part

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
of one paragraph.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.000
So instead, we're going to go ahead

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.000
and add some headings.

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Let me click Edit, and the first thing

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:05.000
that I want to make sure

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.000
you know is that the page title

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:09.000
in Canvas is considered to be

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
heading one.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.000
So when I start making edits, and you'll notice

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.000
that I've got this heading tool right here.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000
Right now it's set to paragraph.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.000
If I click the down arrow,

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:25.000
the first heading available to me

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:28.000
in the page, in that Rich Content Editor

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.000
where I'm creating the page,

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.000
is heading two.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:35.000
Okay. So scrolling down,

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.000
let me scroll down here a little bit.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:40.000
I'm also going to give myself a little

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.000
more real estate by clicking, holding,

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:44.000
and dragging on that array of dots.

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:48.000
And then let's go ahead and scroll down

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:50.000
a little bit further.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:53.000
So, my first heading is

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:55.000
this Introduction to Urban Gardening.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:58.000
Again, with the font that I've got here,

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:00.000
it's really easy to tell that this is

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.000
like a title, but it's not

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.000
for a screen reader.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:06.000
So, I'm going to go ahead

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:09.000
and highlight it, and then up to my heading

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:12.000
tool, I'm going to click the down arrow,

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:15.000
and I choose the highest level,

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:17.000
which is heading two.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:20.000
Now, as soon as I change one

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:23.000
of these headings, Canvas gives me a

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:26.000
default format, but I can actually use

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.000
any format I want.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.000
So, take a look how

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.000
this is designated heading 2.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:35.000
I can make it bold.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:37.000
It is still designated heading 2.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:40.000
I can change the font.

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:42.000
Let's say I want to change it to 36.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:45.000
It is still designated as heading 2.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:48.000
So, you are welcome to use any kind

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:50.000
of formatting that you want.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.000
My recommendation is that

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:55.000
you change the heading type first

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:57.000
and then go ahead and add the formatting

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:59.000
that you want.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:02.000
Let's get this back and do

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:04.000
our other headings.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:06.000
Going down to the next one,

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:09.000
it says, "What is urban gardening?"

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:11.000
Well, "What is urban gardening?"

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:13.000
is one of our subsections.

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:15.000
So, that's going to live under

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:17.000
Introduction to Urban Gardening.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:20.000
So, you can pretty quickly tell

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.000
that our headings are setting up

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:24.000
like an outline,

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:26.000
organizing this information.

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:29.000
Okay. So, let me highlight this

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.000
and I'm going to again

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:33.000
click on that paragraph,

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.000
and I want to change this

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:37.000
to heading three.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:40.000
So, continuing to go down,

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:42.000
I've got another subsection working

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:45.000
on this hierarchy.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.000
Heading two, heading three,

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:49.000
heading four.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:51.000
So, Benefits of Urban Gardening,

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:53.000
that one's going to be

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:55.000
a heading four.

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:57.000
So is Common Challenges.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:00.000
This one is also going to be

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:02.000
heading four.

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:05.000
As I continue to scroll down,

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.000
now I am back to

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:09.000
the next subsection.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:11.000
So, "What is urban gardening?"

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:13.000
If I click on it once,

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:15.000
that was heading three.

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:18.000
This one lives on the same level.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:21.000
So, let me highlight this

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:24.000
and make this one heading three.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:26.000
Now, before I show you

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.000
the next really important step,

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:30.000
I want you to take a look

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:32.000
at that accessibility checker

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:35.000
underneath our Rich Content Editor.

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:38.000
Right now, it doesn't have a number

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.000
circled next to it.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:43.000
And if I click on it, it says,

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:46.000
"No accessibility issues were detected."

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:48.000
However, if I scroll through,

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:50.000
I've got lots of

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:52.000
additional headings that have not yet

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.000
been designated.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:57.000
The accessibility checker, just like

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:59.000
the screen reader, does not know

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:02.000
that these are supposed to be headings.

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:04.000
Now, I'm going to cover

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.000
what the accessibility checker does do

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.000
in terms of headings,

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.000
but I also want to reassure you

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:12.000
that I've got some great

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:14.000
tools for you.

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:16.000
I've got the free

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:18.000
Accessibility Checklist for Canvas.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.000
Take a look at the description

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:22.000
down below.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:24.000
I also have a micro-course

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:26.000
that you can sign up for

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.000
and go through, learning all

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:30.000
of the things to get all

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:33.000
of your content accessible.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:35.000
Okay, let's go back

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:37.000
to headings.

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:39.000
Now, I'm going to get out

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:42.000
of my accessibility checker just for a

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:44.000
second, and I'm actually going to mess

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.000
my hierarchy up.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:49.000
So, remember up here at

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:51.000
Introduction to Urban Gardening,

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.000
I'll click on it once.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.000
This was heading two,

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:58.000
title's heading one, and then

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:00.000
"What is urban gardening?" needed

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:02.000
to be heading three.

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:05.000
But what if I accidentally,

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:08.000
instead of heading three, made this

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:10.000
heading four?

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:12.000
Watch that accessibility checker.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.000
It's now identified an issue,

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:16.000
and it's that hierarchy.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.000
So let's click on it.

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:21.000
And it says, "Heading levels should

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:23.000
not be skipped."

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.000
Okay, let me scroll down

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.000
to the left a little bit.

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:29.000
It's highlighting that

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:31.000
"What is urban gardening?"

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:33.000
That was the problem.

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:36.000
I do not want to leave this as is.

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:38.000
Instead, I want to fix

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.000
that heading hierarchy.

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:43.000
I want to go heading two

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:45.000
and then heading three.

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:47.000
And then we click Apply.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:50.000
Look for those tools and course

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:52.000
down in the description below.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.000
You can learn more

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.000
about accessibility,

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:58.000
starting with this video.
